data.description: This home is one to see! Located in Cavalier Manor this beautiful home has 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths on 1/3 of an acre very spacious inside and out. With brand new flooring throughout, custom cherry cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances there is no attention detail missed inside! Converted garage provides an amazing bonus room that can be used as an extra bedroom, office, or game room. Inside the converted garage you will find a brand new water heater and laundry area. Outside has ample area to be turned into the perfect oasis for this summer! Just minutes from bases and schools making it prime location and easy commute. Schedule your showing today to make this home yours!
